<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4747091>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Distribution of the Burmese species of Cyrtodactylus from the Salween Basin and the phylogenetic relationships of the species of the sinyineensis group. Black circles denote nodes with Bayesian posterior probability (BI) support>0.95 and Maximum Likelihood bootstrap support>95. Grey circles denotes the node with only BI support>0.95." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4747091/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4747085>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Plots of the principal component (PC) analysis ordinations along PC1 and PC2, and PC2 and PC3; and the discriminant analysis of principal components (DAPC) showing the morphospatial relationships of the species of the sinyineensis group." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4747085/files/figure.png" .

